                  </rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-148-victim1501 t18310217-148-viclabel896"></join>. On the Tuesday before the 4th of February I was in the parlour of his house - there is a window, through which I could see a bottle-rack; I saw the prisoner come out of the public-room, and down some stairs, take the tea-pot off the bottle-rack, empty the water out of it, and give it to his wife, who put it into her apron; she went through the yard, then through a shop, and out into the street- the prisoner went up stairs again; I saw the Policeman at the door, and he brought back the woman, with the tea-pot - this is it; I know it by having burnt the lip of it off.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310217-148-person1504">
