                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-constable. I stopped the prisoner's wife with the tea-pot - I then went back, and took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310217-148-person1505">
                  ELIZABETH 
                  WINFIELD
               <interp inst="t18310217-148-person1505" type="surname" value="WINFIELD"></interp>
